 Galvatron nodded. "Yes send a comm to Zardus. Tell him I am the dark one who 
contacted him earlier. And that we apolagize for the disturbance our young 
friend here has made. That he is malfunctioning  but he is one of ours and 
wish him to be given back so we can repair him. Report the situation back to 
me as soon as you get a reply."

--part1_5f.19c1b919.28b66fef_boundary
